snippet.title: [HINDI] BGIS 2024 | GRAND FINALS | Day 3 | BGMI
snippet.description:
Welcome to the GRAND FINALS of the BGIS 2024

Feel the pulse-pounding intensity as the top 16 teams converge on the battleground for a shot at ultimate glory in BGIS history. This is more than just a tournament round, it's the climax of the BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024, where dreams soar and legends are made. With a massive prize pool of INR 2 Crores, the stakes are at their peak.

16 Lan Finalists: GLOBAL ESPORTS, TEAM AARU, X SPARK, iQOO SOUL, FS ESPORTS, VASISTA ESPORTS, TEAM TAMILAS, R4VEN ESPORTS, CARNIVAL GAMING, MOGO ESPORTS, TEAM LIMRA, VENOM GAMING, 8 BIT, TEAM INSANE ESPORTS, INFERNO SQUAD, RECKONING ESPORTS.


#MAKEWAVES #BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIA #INDIAKAGAME #RISEABOVE

snippet.title: Mahua Moitra Returns To Lok Sabha With Fiery Speech, Corners Modi Govt On Manipur, Kashmir & Ayodhya
snippet.description:
TMC Lok Sabha MP Mahua Moitra made her comeback speech while replying to the motion of thanks to the President's address. Notably, the TMC MP was suspended from Lok Sabha just months from elections over cash-for-query allegations. Mahua denied any wrongdoing. And in her comeback speech, she came down heavily on BJP and the Modi government. In her more than half-an-hour-long speech, Mahua cornered BJP over Manipur violence, Kashmir, Ayodhya and many more issues.

snippet.title: Austria 1 - 2 Turkiye | Highlights | UEFA Euro | 3rd July 2024
snippet.description:
In the UEFA Euro 2024, Austria and Turkiye faced each other in the round of 16. Turkiye found the back of the net in just one minute and started the game strongly. Demiral extended the lead in the 59th minute for Turkiye but Austria was able to score one back later in the match. In the end, Turkiye found a hard-fought victory and moved into the quarter-finals.

snippet.title: 'Manipur Burning, Govt a Mute Spectator For a Year': What Opposition Said on Manipur in Parliament
snippet.description:
Several opposition leaders, in the motion of thanks on the President's Address in Lok Sabha, slammed the government over Manipur Violence. Inner Manipur MP from Congress party, Angomcha Bimol Akoijam said the government had been a "mute spectator" on the Manipur violence for over a year. Leader of Opposition, Rahul Gandhi asked the PM why he hasn't visited Manipur ever since the violence started there in May 2023. TMC MP Mahua Moitra also slammed the government for not stopping the violence in a "burning Manipur".
#manipur #parliament #manipurviolence #loksabha

Music: BMG

snippet.title: Indian Family and Foreigner  | Take A Break x @BhaDiPa
snippet.description:
Brace yourself for a comedy spectacle in our latest sketch, "Indian Family and Foreigner"! 😂🏡
In this side-splitting episode, we delve into the chaos that ensues when an Indian family plays host to a special guest – a Canadian colleague of the family's father. What starts as a simple visit quickly spirals into an uproarious whirlwind of cultural misunderstandings, hospitality overload, and neighborhood mayhem.
#LaughOutLoud #YouTubeSketch

It was a nice experience of working with Paula McGlynn from @BhaDiPa if you like this collab please let us know in comments.😇🙌

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4126: Popatlal Ki Kismat
--------------------------------------------------------
With Inspector Pandey and his wife by his side, Popatlal meets his potential bride and her family. Will this crucial meeting pave the way for Popatlal's marriage to finally happen?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4126 | 2 July 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Episode 4126: Popatlal Ki Kismat
--------------------------------------------------------
With Inspector Pandey and his wife by his side, Popatlal meets his potential bride and her family. Will this crucial meeting pave the way for Popatlal's marriage to finally happen?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4126 | 2 July 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: रामकथा - कथा मन्दाकिनी | Dr Kumar Vishwas | Rishikesh | Apne Apne Ram
snippet.description:
विगत दिनों ऋषिकेश के विश्व-प्रसिद्ध त्रिवेणी घाट पर सदानीरा मॉं गंगा और राम कथा की पुण्य धारा के संगम का सुयोग बना था। उस रात देव नदी की दिव्य-धाराओं के सानिध्य ने मुझे माध्यम बनाकर रामकथा मंदाकिनी की धारा को जो अपूर्व प्रवाह सौंपा वह स्वयं मेरे लिए भी किसी चमत्कार से कम नहीं था। उस पवित्र-योग के पुण्य-प्रसाद स्वरूप उस ऊर्जा-सत्र का यह अंश आप सभी आस्थावानों को सादर समर्पित है। 🙏🏻❤️
#kumarvishwas #ganga #rishikesh #haridwar 
00:00 भगवान राम के पूर्वज त्रिशंकु
03:50 मम तनु-वितरण-समये हरता देया न मे हरिता (रहीम)
10:35 क्यों कपिल मुनि ने राजा सगर के पुत्रों को भस्म किया था?
15:35 भजमन राम चरण सुखदाई


Follow us on :- 

YouTube :- http://youtube.com/KumarVishwas
Facebook :- https://www.facebook.com/KumarVishwas
Twitter :- https://twitter.com/DrKumarVishwas
Instagram :- https://www.instagram.com/KumarVishwas

Subscribe To Our Other YouTube Channels:-

Apne Apne Ram    : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneRamOfficial
  
The KV Studio        : https://www.youtube.com/@TheKVStudio

Apne Apne Shyam : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneShyamOfficial

-------------------------------------------------------------------
About Dr Kumar Vishwas :

The people who make history are the ones who not only give their life to their career but also give their career a new life. When the career is that of a poet, every step is a risk. Kumar Vishwas is one such poet who has gifted himself an era of such a popularity which other poets cant’t even dream of.
Kumar Vishwas is a poet who went beyond the stereotypical norms of ‘Kavi Sammelan’ or poetic functions and made it a performer’s stage. He has mastered and excelled in all aspects in whatever he has done. Dr Kumar Vishwas has been doing this since years just with a mic and his poems and wits in his soulful voice.
His popularity can be guessed by the fact that the audience sings his verses with him, he has crafted a new dimension by rejuvenating the structure and mechanics of Hindi poetry and Kavi Sammelan.
 
Recently, Dr. Kumar Vishwas has started hosting energy sessions popularly Known as Apne Apne Ram and Apne Apne Shyam where he talks about life skills of Shri Ram’s and Shri Krishna's life, and the applicability of the same in one’s own life to over come the challenges and social concerns we come across in our life.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.title: Keerai Thokku Recipe in Tamil | Spinach Gravy Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make keerai thokku recipe in tamil. This is a healthy recipe which is very tasty and the main star of the dish is fresh green spinach leaves. We have to make sure that the spinach is cooked just right and not too much that they brown and wither. This side dish can be served along with white rice and can also be served as a side dish for chapathi / dosa or idli.
#keeraithokku #keerairecipe #keeraikootu 

Friends, please do try this spinach gravy at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!


Ingredients for Keerai Thokku:
For grinding:
1 tsp Oil
1 tbsp Channa dal
1 tbsp Coriander seeds
1 tsp Cumin seeds
1 tsp Oil
1 Onion
6-7 Garlic cloves
1/5 tsp Chilli powder
1/2 Tomato
1 small piece Tamarind

1 tbsp Oil
1/4 tsp Mustard seeds
4-5 fenugreek
4-5 garlic cloves
2 red chilli
Curry leaves
250g spinch
required Salt
1-2 tbsp Oil extra

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | નઈ બને તારે મારે | Nai Bane Tare Mare | 2024 New Gujarati Song | નવું ગુજરાતી ગીત
snippet.description:
Groove to the upbeat tunes of Rakesh Barot's new Gujarati song "નઈ બને તારે મારે," available now on @SaregamaGujarati 

Singer: Rakesh Barot
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Singer: Rakesh Barot
Artist: Rakesh Barot,Sudha Tripathi
Music: Rahul Nadiya , Ravi Nagar
Lyrics: Vipul Raval
Creative Head : Dhyey Films & Team
DOP-Editing: Chirag kachhadiya 
Production: Satubha. 
Spot: Raju n akshay 
Choreographer: Dipak turi 
Concept n director: Pranav jethva 
Technically Support: Jenish Talaviya
Hair makeup: Hasmukh 
Light: Kalpesh jadav

તુ મને બાળવા  ફરે  જાનુ બીજાની હારે …(૨)
તું આવું રે કરી ખોટા  દેખાવ કેમ કરે …
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે ખોટા ખેલ ચમ તું કરે ,મને ફેર કઈ નઈ પડે (૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે
તારા જેવી છોડીયો મને સત્તર રે ભડકોની ,
મારા શોમુ ઇનુ ઉતરી ગિયું છે પોની ,
ઓ તુ મને પડવા ફરે એવુ કોઈ કાળે નહીં થાવનું ,
ઉતરી જરે અભિમાન તારે મોપ માં રહેવાનું ..
ભલે તું મને હેરાન કરે મારી પાછળ પાછળ ફરે (૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
ઓ મને  ને ભાળી તું તો નખરા ઘણા કરે ,
તને એમ લગતું હશે મારા પર મરે છે ,
ઓ તારો ઠાઠ નજારો જોઈ હું પીગળી નહિ જવાનો ,
તારી પાછળ હુ ગોંડો નહિ થાવનો ,
તને હું પડીશ બહુ ભારે ,તુ જતી રે તારા ઘરે ,(૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,(2)
 
 
#નઈબનેતારેમારે
#NaiBaneTareMare
#rakeshbarot 
#saregamagujarati 
#rakeshbarotnewsong 
#gujaratisongs   
#gujaratilovesong  
#gujarati 
#ગુજરાતીગીત

snippet.title: Athers and Nasser REACT to India's incredible T20 World Cup win! 🏆 | Sky Sports Cricket Vodcast
snippet.description:

Jaan Nisar Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 30th June 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

Welcome to Cheeky Cheeka!

🎉 In This Episode: T20 World Cup Triumph! 🏆 

Join our experts Cheeka and Ani and our special guest Nanee as we dive into the thrilling final of the T20 World Cup where India emerged victorious against South Africa! 🇮🇳🏏

✨ Highlights:
- Rohit Sharma, Virat Kohli, and Hardik Pandya's Redemption Story
- Bumrah: The Man with the Golden Arm
- Suryakumar Yadav's Catch of the Tournament
- Emotional moments and celebrations as India lifts the T20 World Cup trophy after 17 years!
- Virat Kohli Retires from the T20i as a Champion.

Relive the excitement, the drama, and the unforgettable winning moments with us. Don't miss out on this epic discussion!

snippet.title: Dhilluku Dhuddu - Comedy Scenes | Santhanam Super Hit Counters | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
Kumar and Kajal are in love but her father is against the match and tries to have Kumar killed with the help of Mani. Things go awry when Mani invites Kumar's family to a haunted house. 

Dhilluku Dhuddu  is a 2016 Indian Tamil-language comedy horror film directed by Rambala and produced by Sri Thenandal Films. The film features starring Santhanam and Anchal Singh in the leading roles, while Saurabh Shukla appears in a pivotal role. Featuring music composed by S. Thaman, Dhilluku Dhuddu began production in November 2015 and released on 7 July 2016 to positive response and turned to be successful at box office.[3][4][5] The film was later dubbed in Hindi as Raj Mahal 3 in 2017. The film was dubbed in Telugu as Dammunte Sommera in 2018.[6] The film was remade in Kannada in 2019 as Gimmick starring Ganesh.

snippet.title: Tuition Days | E03 - Ishq Ke Side Effects | Krutika Deo, Chirag Katrecha & Aaryan Prajapati | RVCJ
snippet.description:
Kaisa bhi ho Sawaal,
Sahi jawaab OSWAAL!
Prepare smarter for your exams with Oswaal Books! No.1 choice of teachers & students for School, Entrance & Competitive exam preparation. CBSE | ICSE | Olympiads | JEE | NEET | CUET | CLAT | CAT | UPSC | Defence | Gov. Exams and more.

Use coupon code TUITIONDAYS to claim additional 20% off on all Oswaal Books. - https://www.oswaalbooks.com/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=tuitiondays

Dive into the Third episode of Tuition Days - Ishq Ke Side Effects

In Episode 3 of Tuition Days, we see Resham and Tanay's bond growing with Girgit's help. Akshat discovers their relationship, leading to rising tensions. Tanay’s sister supports them, but an unexpected twist leaves their future uncertain. Will Resham and Tanay end up together?
Join us for an episode filled with friendship, drama, and surprises. 

"Tuition Days" centers on Tanay, a math genius, and his mischievous friend Girgit as they navigate the ups and downs of home tuition. The arrival of new student Resham, who quickly becomes Tanay’s crush, stirs things up. With the charm of home tutoring in a world of big coaching centers, Tanay strives to make his teacher proud. 
However, unexpected twists keep everyone on their toes. Enjoy a delightful mix of friendship, love, and school life in "Tuition Days.

snippet.title: பாறை மீன் குழம்பும் பாஸ்மதி அரிசி சோறும்!| Amma Makes Traditional Fish Curry with Dubar Basmati Rice
snippet.description:
அப்பா பிடித்து குடுத்த மீனை வைத்து அம்மா இன்று பாசுமதி அரிசி சோறுடன், பாறை மீன் குழம்பு வைத்து  குடுத்தாங்க.

 சுவாரஸ்யமா இன்று பாயசமும் பாசுமதி அரிசியில செஞ்சு குடுத்தாங்க.

பாசுமதி அரிசியை எப்படி பயன்படுத்தணும்னு அம்மா இந்த வீடியோல விளக்கமா சொல்றாங்க, இந்தியாகேட் பாஸ்மதி அரிசிய வச்சு இதேமாதிரி உங்களுக்குப் பிடிச்ச உணவு வகைகளையும் செய்து பார்க்கலாம். நீங்களும் உங்கள் வீட்டில் முயற்சி செய்தால் கமெண்டில் எங்களுக்கு தெரியப்படுத்தவும்!

#experimentswithbasmati #indiagatefoods

snippet.title: Stepaa Maar Song Tomorrow  | Double ISMART | RAmPothineni | Puri Jagannadh| Charmme Kaur
snippet.description:
Seeti Maar shots straight from the sets 🤙
Get ready for the Sensational #STEPPAMAAR to take over the Masses with a Bang 💥

Double ISMART First Single out Tomorrow at 4 PM 🎶🔥

#DoubleISMART is an Indian Action Entertainer film, written and directed by Puri Jagannnadh featuring Ram Pothineni in the lead role will be seen in a Massier character than iSmart Shankar. Also stars Sanjay Dutt, Kavya Thapar in the prominent roles. Produced by Puri Jagannadh and Charmme Kaur under Puri Connects, The film will have a much bigger span and will be made with a high budget on a large scale with top-class technical standards. Double iSmart will be releasing worldwide on AUGUST 15th,2024  in Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam, and Hindi languages.

Movie Details:
Cast: Ram Pothineni, Sanjay Dutt, Kavya Thapar, Bani J, Ali, Getup Sreenu, Sayaji Shinde, Makrand Deshpande,  Temper Vamsi & others.

snippet.title: 1 कप गेंहू के आटे से गरमागरम मजेदार नाश्ता बनाइए और समोसा कचोरी भूल जाइए - ATTA KE KHASTA NASHTA
snippet.description:
#breakfast #kachori #barish 


INGREDIENTS TO MAKE THE DOUGH 

2 Tbsp Barik Suji 
3/4 Cup Water 
1 tsp Salt 
1 Tbsp Desi Ghee 
1 tsp Red Chilli Flakes 
1/4 tsp Ajwian 
1 tsp Sesame 
Fresh Coriander Leaves 
1 Cup Whole Wheat Flour 

INGREDIENTS TO MAKE STUFFING 

1/2 Cup Sev 
1 Cup Poha 
2 Tbsp oil 
1 Pinch Hing 
1 tsp Mustard Seeds
1 tsp Jeera 
1/2 tsp Sauf 
1 tsp Coriander Seeds 
5 - 6 Garlic Cloves Chopped 
1/4 tsp Baking soda
1 tsp Red Chilli Powder 
1/2 tsp Haldi Powder 
1 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
1 tsp Salt 
2 Onions
3-5 Green Chillies 
2 tsp Amchoor Powder
